<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }
      body {
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
        background-color:#cfcdcd;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .content {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .message {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #303031;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .sender {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        color: #888888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1 class="title">Welcome to Vertives - Your Social Networking Hub!</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <p class="message">Hello, <b><%= username %>!</b></p>
        <p class="message">
          Welcome to Vertives, the vibrant and dynamic social networking
          platform where connections, creativity, and community come together!
          We are absolutely thrilled to have you on board and excited to embark
          on this journey with you. At Vertives, our mission is to provide a
          seamless and enjoyable experience for all our users, enabling you to
          connect with friends, family, colleagues, and like-minded individuals
          from around the globe. Whether you're here to share your thoughts,
          explore new interests, or simply have fun, Vertives has something to
          offer for everyone.
        </p>
        <p class="message">
          Happy networking!
        </p>
        <p class="message">
          Best regards,
          <br />
          <span class="sender"><%= sender %></span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Vertives. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
